ygData.messageBody:
Hi all,
As I have read the boards over the last couple of weeks, I can't
help but get the feeling that I am the old man of this group. I have
been playing EQ since the beginning, and have a vast knowledge of the
game. I current have 3 characters, a 65 Ranger, a 48 Necro, and a 44
Rogue. I have, however, played every class into the 30's, just to get
a feel for how each class works. Please feel free to ask me any
questions =) I check the boards once every three days, and will try
to answer any questions I can =)

Rhemy DeMortis
65 Forest Stalker of Tunare
Officer and Proud member of Haven's Promise
Mith Marr server
